text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 25.7.6, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), Cumulative List (Publication 78).

The material relating to Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook EO/BMF previously contained in IRM section 25.7.6, Section 6, Cumulative List (Publication 78) is incorporated into IRM 25.7.1, starting at IRM 25.7.1.15, continuing through IRM 25.7.1.17.
This supersedes and obsoletes IRM 25.7.6, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), Cumulative List (Publication 78), dated January 1, 2018.
Jennifer A. Jett Director, Business Systems Planning Shared Services Tax Exempt and Government Entities
